    "description": "In a procedural generated natural environment, you, the hunter, while survive by grip life-size weapons against giant monsters and creating new weapons and armor with the materials you obtain.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/6db61b24fa7324028b567066adb554b7.poster.avif?t=1771316464\" width=512 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/6db61b24fa7324028b567066adb554b7.webm?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/6db61b24fa7324028b567066adb554b7.mp4?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Strip materials from monsters to obtain powerful weapons and armor, and Let's go in search of prey for more power.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/d5c857ab2858b0729a4987867e06e03b.poster.avif?t=1771316464\" width=512 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/d5c857ab2858b0729a4987867e06e03b.webm?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/d5c857ab2858b0729a4987867e06e03b.mp4?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Because of the concepts of weather, temperature, and seasons, hunters must protect themselves from a variety of environmental factors.<br>Changes will also occur in the monsters that appear. Your ability to adapt to the environment will be tested.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/af5dfea1d56512fa9bd6d5b5148f6c77.poster.avif?t=1771316464\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/af5dfea1d56512fa9bd6d5b5148f6c77.webm?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/af5dfea1d56512fa9bd6d5b5148f6c77.mp4?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Initial supplies are limited, so gather materials and build a base as soon as possible. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/2688568b34db59aaec8ef63572779c44.poster.avif?t=1771316464\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/2688568b34db59aaec8ef63572779c44.webm?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/2688568b34db59aaec8ef63572779c44.mp4?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In order to fight powerful monsters, hunters must build a safe base, secure food supplies, and be well-prepared.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/899c42c6f34bec7ab99f04fc910b436c.poster.avif?t=1771316464\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/899c42c6f34bec7ab99f04fc910b436c.webm?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2120560/extras/899c42c6f34bec7ab99f04fc910b436c.mp4?t=1771316464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
